<P>Then lay at &s;<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 letter">ake his earthly all&mdash;His <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 letter">ee &s;imple e&s;tate in his native <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 letter">oil&mdash;his precious life&mdash;his honour &s;uperior to both&mdash;his country dearer than all.</P>
